1933, page 54.
</font>
</blockquote>
<p>
<font color="blue">
<i>Again, we see the warning about people taking pride in their sins:</i>
</font>
<font color="#4f007f">
&quot;My sins were much bigger and more outrageous than your wimpy-ass little sins.&quot;
