from Frank Buchman and his lieutenants, then such erroneous Guidance
must have come from <i><b>The Evil One</b></i>, not God.
In that way, no follower could get a message from God like,
<font color="blue">
<i>&quot;Frank Buchman is crazy. Quit this stupid cult right now.&quot;</i></font>
